the Lorde. Again,<NOTE PLACE="marg">Reg. vii,</NOTE> when the
<PB REF="12">
Israelites gathered together a<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">
Mizpha, lamentiug their sinnes
and prayinge vnto the Lorde for
healpe againste the Philistines,
