this maner did the Apo<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">tles after
Christes ascension &amp; many other
<PB REF="13">
godlye menne in the primatyue
church fast, So that their custom
was on that daye that they dyd
fast, to eat nothing til night, but
to occupy them selues about such
godlye exersyes, as here to fore
are mencioned.</P>
</DIV2>
<DIV2 N="3" TYPE="chapter">
<HEAD>The .iii. Chapter</HEAD>
<P>ANd as the godlye menne in
