broughte to passe, godly &amp; Chri|sten
abstinence shall healp great+lye.<NOTE PLACE="marg">Fastynge tameth the flesh.</NOTE>
For there is nothinge that so
tameth and bringeth vnder the
wylde and vnrulye lustes of the
flesh, as fasting and abstine~ce, e|uen
as there is nothing that ma|keth
